156
00:12:54,630 --> 00:12:56,080
yet it also becomes

157
00:12:56,670 --> 00:12:58,030
the reason you stay on the force.

158
00:13:00,270 --> 00:13:01,670
I remember you said back then

159
00:13:02,390 --> 00:13:03,390
