00:14:38,510 --> 00:14:41,000
just past 20.

185
00:14:43,870 --> 00:14:45,360
Her life had barely started.

186
00:14:45,550 --> 00:14:47,030
Those traffickers

187
00:14:47,550 --> 00:14:49,270
and Lu Youliang destroyed it.

188
00:14:51,080 --> 00:14:52,270
After she was rescued,

189
00:14:53,030 --> 00:14:54,630
