222
00:16:06,770 --> 00:16:07,650
(Sold to Lu Youliang)

223
00:16:07,650 --> 00:16:08,600
(Died after a burglary)

224
00:16:08,600 --> 00:16:09,600
Lu Youliang was sentenced

225
00:16:09,600 --> 00:16:10,440
for that reason.

226
