237
00:16:42,600 --> 00:16:43,910
Yesterday, Xu Jingzhi got

238
00:16:43,910 --> 00:16:45,120
Zhuang Mingcheng's

239
00:16:45,120 --> 00:16:46,270
DNA test result.

240
00:16:46,480 --> 00:16:47,360
