242
00:17:03,480 --> 00:17:04,400
Lu Ran

243
00:17:04,680 --> 00:17:07,350
was born in Lujia Village, Wuyang.

244
00:17:07,920 --> 00:17:09,000
His father is Lu Youliang;

245
00:17:09,000 --> 00:17:10,680
his mother is Wu Min.

246
00:17:11,600 --> 00:17:13,270
Wu Min, a Yunling native,

247
00:17:13,640 --> 00:17:15,070
