248
00:17:15,550 --> 00:17:17,000
During freshman break,

249
00:17:17,000 --> 00:17:19,110
she was abducted by Jiang Yongquan

250
00:17:19,240 --> 00:17:20,200
and sold to Lu Youliang.

251
00:17:20,200 --> 00:17:22,160
There, she gave birth to Lu Ran.

252
00:17:23,070 --> 00:17:25,440
Throughout childhood, Lu Ran suffered

253
00:17:25,960 --> 00:17:26,800
domestic violence

254
00:17:27,400 --> 00:17:29,110
