255
00:17:29,110 --> 00:17:31,160
repeatedly rape his mother,

256
00:17:32,000 --> 00:17:33,720
receiving no healthy

257
00:17:33,720 --> 00:17:34,720
emotional feedback,

258
00:17:35,070 --> 00:17:37,400
so his psyche grew twisted.

259
00:17:38,590 --> 00:17:40,550
In Lu Ran's final year of high school,

260
00:17:41,270 --> 00:17:42,480
Wu Min died

261
00:17:42,790 --> 00:17:44,160
in a burglary.

262
00:17:44,510 --> 00:17:46,550
Later, Lu Ran went abroad

263
00:17:46,550 --> 00:17:48,070
to study chemistry.

264
00:17:49,440 --> 00:17:50,310
Five years ago,

265
00:17:51,170 --> 00:17:52,530
Lu Ran died overseas.

266
00:17:54,160 --> 00:17:55,640
Lu Youliang was still in prison.

267
00:17:56,030 --> 00:17:58,030
He didn't even know

268
00:17:58,030 --> 00:17:59,120
Lu Ran had left the country.

269
00:17:59,790 --> 00:18:01,720
He came to me probably for money

270
00:18:01,960 --> 00:18:03,110
and his son,

271
00:18:03,730 --> 00:18:05,790
