who'd been tailing me,

272
00:18:05,790 --> 00:18:06,880
would spot him.

273
00:18:07,640 --> 00:18:08,510
Actually,

274
00:18:08,510 --> 00:18:10,350
the real Zhuang Mingcheng

275
00:18:10,790 --> 00:18:11,990
inherited his parents' company

276
00:18:11,990 --> 00:18:12,790
after their death.

277
00:18:12,790 --> 00:18:15,000
It's a foreign gene-database

278
00:18:15,000 --> 00:18:16,200
storage firm.

279
00:18:16,830 --> 00:18:19,110
That let Zhuang Mingcheng swap

280
00:18:19,270 --> 00:18:21,000
his data with Lu Ran's.

281
00:18:21,580 --> 00:18:22,440
Lu Ran exploited

282
00:18:22,440 --> 00:18:23,720
Zhuang Mingcheng's depression

283
00:18:23,720 --> 00:18:25,880
and used a lab explosion

284
00:18:25,880 --> 00:18:27,310
to drive him to suicide.

285
00:18:27,880 --> 00:18:29,030
Later,

286
00:18:29,390 --> 00:18:30,880
