after plastic surgery,

287
00:18:30,880 --> 00:18:32,550
Lu Ran took Zhuang's identity

288
00:18:32,550 --> 00:18:33,720
and returned to Wuyang.

289
00:18:34,450 --> 00:18:35,310
I once took a call

290
00:18:35,310 --> 00:18:36,350
from Lu Youliang.

291
00:18:36,550 --> 00:18:37,790
Thinking back, I believe

292
00:18:37,790 --> 00:18:38,960
Lu Ran must've left it for me.

293
00:18:39,960 --> 00:18:41,720
Lu Ran's hatred for Lu Youliang

294
00:18:42,240 --> 00:18:43,880
